1. Clone https://github.com/harsha-simhadri/big-ann-benchmarks into related/big-ann-benchmarks
2. Clone https://github.com/erikbern/ann-benchmarks into related/ann-benchmarks
3. cd related/ann-benchmarks && python create_dataset.py --dataset sift-128-euclidean
4. cd related/big-ann-benchmarks python create_dataset.py --dataset yfcc-10M   

To export yfcc:
'''
python generate_parquet.py ../../related/big-ann-benchmarks/data/yfcc100M/base.10M.u8bin parquet/base100K.parquet -v -l 100000
python generate_parquet.py ../../related/big-ann-benchmarks/data/yfcc100M/query.public.100K.u8bin parquet/query1K.parquet -v -l 1000
python generate_parquet.py ../../related/big-ann-benchmarks/data/yfcc100M/GT.public.ibin parquet/GT1K.parquet -v -l 1000
'''